Package chav1961.purelib.basic.annotations

This package contains all annotations for the basic abilities of the library

See: Description

  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    ConsoleCommand
    This annotation is used to mark a method to call from the Console manager.
    ConsoleCommandParameter
    This annotation is used to associate the method parameters and console command variable.
    ConsoleCommandPrefix
    This annotation is used to mark a class as console command processor for the Console manager.
